0) Middleware
1) add logger middleware (npm i redux-logger)
2) create own logger (npm deep-object-diff)
3) connect thunk (npm install redux-thunk)
4) run local server (npm init, npm install json-server, touch db.json, json-server --watch db.json --port 5001)
5) create async action
6) get request
7) post request
8) delete request
9) put request
10) loaders and errors